@startuml passenger_seat_cmd_to_seat_pass_position_comfort_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Passenger Seat Cmd To SEAT PASS Position Comfort Signal Flow\n(passenger seat-control command + vehicle state -> passenger seat position / heat / ventilation state)

participant "Seat-control bus" as SeatCtl #F4F7FB
participant "Vehicle state bus" as Veh #E8F0FE
participant "SEAT_PASS\npassenger-seat owner" as SeatPass #E8F7E8
participant "Passenger-seat state bus" as SeatBus #FFF4CC
participant "Observers /\ncomfort readers" as Obs #FCE8FF

== Passenger Seat Inputs ==

SeatCtl -> SeatPass : frmSeatControlMsg\nPassengerSeatCmd / SeatHeatLevel / SeatVentLevel
Veh -> SeatPass : frmVehicleStateCanMsg\ngDriveState
activate SeatPass
SeatPass -> SeatPass : seatCtrlInputStale =\nethIsRecentTick(gSeatCtrlRxMs, 300)
SeatPass -> SeatPass : vehicleInputStale =\nethIsRecentTick(gVehicleRxMs, 300)
SeatPass -> SeatPass : if seat-control stale then\nseatCmd = 0 / heat = 0 / vent = 0
SeatPass -> SeatPass : if vehicle stale then\ndriveState = 3
SeatPass -> SeatPass : position changes only when\ndriveState == 0
SeatPass -> SeatPass : applySeatDelta() moves\nSeatPassPos by +/-5 per command step
note right of SeatPass
Representative gating inputs
- PassengerSeatCmd
- SeatHeatLevel
- SeatVentLevel
- gDriveState
end note

== Passenger Seat Publish ==

SeatPass -> SeatBus : frmSeatPassStateMsg\nSeatPassPos / SeatPassHeatLvl / SeatPassVentLvl
note right of SeatPass
Representative outputs
- SeatPassPos
- SeatPassHeatLvl
- SeatPassVentLvl
end note

== Downstream Visibility ==

SeatBus -> Obs : passenger-seat comfort visibility /\nseat and cabin observers
deactivate SeatPass

note over SeatCtl, Obs
Representative runtime chain
1. Passenger seat-control command and vehicle state reach SEAT_PASS
2. SEAT_PASS applies freshness gates and parked-only motion rule
3. SEAT_PASS updates seat position and comfort levels
4. SEAT_PASS publishes passenger-seat state for downstream readers
end note

@enduml
